@1297 = ~[PC] (You decide to follow him.)~
@1298 = ~[PC] (You decide you would never intrude on his privacy by following him down to the water.)~
@1299 = ~[PC] (You take advantage of the opportunity to rummage through his pack.)~
@1300 = ~[ARAN] Hey, there, I got a question for you. Do you mind if I rummage about in your undergarments a bit, an' poke through your stuff? Mayhap I can ink up some o' your gear, random like?~ [c-aws107]
@1301 = ~[PC] I meant no harm. You scribble and scrawl all the time, and I was just curious. I want to know what is going on.~
@1302 = ~[PC] I want to know if any member of this party is discussing anything with the outside world. Even little things.~
@1303 = ~[PC] Don't keep any secrets from me. I will not be happy if you hide anything, anything at all.~
@1304 = ~[PC] Well, perhaps I went a little overboard. But I don't like to be kept in the dark, and it seems like you are writing things I should know about.~
@1305 = ~[PC] I hold the coin for the party. I want to know how you are using it, and to what purpose.~
@1306 = ~[ARAN] Hey, there, I got a question for you. Do you know who has been messin' about in my pack, smudgin' up my writin' space?~ [c-aws108]
@1307 = ~[PC] Yes, I do. I did. What are these letters you keep writing all about?~
@1308 = ~[PC] No, I don't.~
@1309 = ~[PC] You must be mistaken. I did not leave a single smudge or telltale sign of my browsing.~
@1310 = ~[PC] Search me.~
@1311 = ~[ARAN] Aye, then. Shuttin' up.~
@1312 = ~[ARAN] By the Cryin' God's tears, you are in a mood.~
@1313 = ~[ARAN] Sure.~
@1314 = ~[ARAN] Fine. I'll be over there.~
@1315 = ~[ARAN] Sune's Lusty Lips, you can sure kill a conversation.~
@1316 = ~[ARAN] Corellon's Bowhand, you have an attitude today.~
@1317 = ~[ARAN] Shar's Arsehole, shut me down, will ya? Fine.~
@1318 = ~[ARAN] By the Cryin' God's Tears - I was just makin' conversation.~
@1319 = ~[ARAN] Well, I'll just bugger off, then. This is me, see, mindin' my own business.~
@1320 = ~[ARAN] Cyric's Twisted Tongue. Just wanted to talk, y'know.~
