@1323 = ~[ARAN] Lolth's Cruel Fingernails, you can cut a man down. Sure. Shuttin' up.~
@1324 = ~[ARAN] Umberlee's Fickle Breath, I'll shut my blighted mouth, then.~
@1325 = ~[ARAN] Malar's Sharp Teeth. Shuttin' up an' soldierin'.~
@1326 = ~[ARAN] Tiamat's Grasping Hands. You don't want to talk, fine by me.~
