@1329 = ~[ARAN] Shaundakul's Mighty Breath, I guess I was yammerin' on again.~
@1330 = ~[ARAN] Well, that was colder than Auril's Tits in th' Ten Towns. Shuttin' up.~
@1331 = ~[ARAN] Kelemvor's Scythe - you cut me off quick, there, <CHARNAME>.~
@1332 = ~[ARAN] Bane's Broken Bones, but you are in a mood.~
