@1533 = ~[ARAN] Well, my mother done taught me right. If a lady needs somethin', don't talk back - just do what she be askin'. Saves a heap o' trouble, it does. Except that time when I done what th' lady asked, only to find out there should have been a mite bit more communication with her husband...~
