@3359 = ~[ARAN] It scares a man to his marrow when you see some child standin' in the remains o' their village, holdin' a bloodsoaked doll in one hand an' the remains o' her older sister in th' other. The Chill liked to play wi' their captives in some ugly ways. It was worse when they left some o' th' young ones alive after they was finished.~
