@3443 = ~[ARAN] Well, if you don't, then I guess you don't. But you sure spend a lot of time wi' a certain gentleman 'friend', eh? I'm not always th' sharpest tack in th' barrel, but it seems like you have need o' some companionship. Guess that means there be somethin' inside even after your soul gets torn out. You must be stronger than Corellon's Bowhand.~
