@8125 = ~[PC] No war. Besides, I have ways of distracting your attention. Like these clothes of mine, and how they seem to have found their way off of my body and flown up onto the bank all by themselves.~
@8126 = ~[ARAN] (There is a tremendous splash as Aran dives in close to you. His strong hands grip your your torso as he rapidly lifts you out of the water.)~
@8127 = ~[PC] (Spit a long stream of water into his face, and grin.)~
@8128 = ~[PC] (Slap him.)~
@8129 = ~[PC] That is more than enough roughhousing, thank you. I'm headed back to camp.~
