@8131 = ~[ARAN] Hey, warn a lad, eh? I didn't rightly hear you.~
@8132 = ~[PC] Going for a swim?~
@8133 = ~[PC] That looks very... inviting.~
@8134 = ~[PC] That looks very... cold.~
@8135 = ~[PC] Tactical error on your part, I think. This bundle of clothes seems to belong to you, yet you are all the way over there.~
@8136 = ~[PC] You enjoy yourself. I'm headed back to camp. Don't catch cold.~
@8137 = ~[PC] (Sit on the bank, watching him.)~
@8138 = ~[ARAN] (There is a small pile of gear tidily set a comfortable distance from the edge of the water. Aran is splashing about and singing lustily, with lyrics not usually meant for polite company...)~
@8139 = ~[PC] Splashing about all alone, are we?~
@8140 = ~[PC] Hmmm. This bundle of clothes seems to belong to you, yet you are all the way over there.~
@8141 = ~[PC] You enjoy yourself. I'm headed back to camp. By the way, those lyrics are... interesting.~
@8142 = ~[ARAN] Well, it surely do look that way, eh? You could join me, but I figure I ought to warn you I wasn't expectin' no company. So I didn't take naught in th' way o' precautions for modesty.~
@8143 = ~[PC] Modesty is overrated. (Strip off your clothing and dive into the water next to him.)~
@8144 = ~[PC] I don't mind. (Strip down to your underthings and carefully wade out into the water.)~
@8145 = ~[ARAN] Well, it is. Feels good to have a swim, it does. You could join me, but I figure I ought to warn you I wasn't expectin' no company. So I didn't take naught in th' way o' precautions for modesty.~
@8146 = ~[PC] It looks like it might be fun.~
@8147 = ~[PC] That also looks very... cold.~
@8148 = ~[ARAN] Oi, watch where you be directin' that gaze, eh? You could join me, but I figure I ought to warn you I wasn't expectin' no company. So I didn't take naught in th' way o' precautions for modesty.~
@8149 = ~[PC] Very cold, I think.~
@8150 = ~[ARAN] You wouldn't.~
@8151 = ~[PC] (Grin at him, and pick up the bundle of clothes.)~
@8152 = ~[PC] Perhaps I might, perhaps I might not. But to assure you I am a woman of good conscience, I will leave some hostages as a token of my goodwill. (Strip slowly, carefully, putting your clothes next to his before wading in toward him.)~
@8153 = ~[PC] I wouldn't do anything as rash as... ooops. Sorry. I think they fell in the water.~
@8154 = ~[PC] (Strip off your clothing and dive into the water next to him.)~
@8155 = ~[PC] No, I wouldn't. But you should have seen your face. (Sit on the bank, watching him.)~
@8156 = ~[PC] I might. Then again, I might not.~
@8157 = ~[ARAN] (His grin is broad as he swims away from you, long lean arms flicking a fine spray of water droplets into the air.)~
@8158 = ~[ARAN] (He settles into a steady rhythm for a while, powerful stokes speeding him along, occasionally exposing a brief flash of buttock as he turns. Eventually, he slows and treads water, studying you.)~
@8159 = ~[PC] What are you looking at?~
@8160 = ~[PC] Come on, we should get going.~
@8161 = ~[PC] You call that swimming?~
@8162 = ~[PC] (Watch him carefully, idly playing with a leather strap on his gear.)~
@8163 = ~[ARAN] Now I don't know whether to be happy on account o' you have th' most beautiful breasts a man ever did see, or unhappy on account o' you just splashed me.~
@8164 = ~[PC] You know, that was a little forward. We are just having a swim.~
@8165 = ~[PC] (Swim to him and snuggle close to his back.) There. Now you can't see anything. Modesty is preserved.~
@8166 = ~[PC] (Swim to him and face him, wrapping your arms around his neck.) Are you sure they are beautiful?~
@8167 = ~[PC] (Swim to him and wrap your arms around his neck.)~
@8168 = ~[PC] (Swim slowly around him.)~
@8169 = ~[PC] Oh, forget it. You always spoil things with your clumsy passes. I'm headed back to camp.~
@8170 = ~[ARAN] (He settles into a steady rhythm for awhile, powerful stokes speeding him along, occasionally exposing a brief flash of buttock as he turns. Eventually, he slows and treads water, studying you.)~
@8171 = ~[PC] Hey, I didn't say I would swim. You keep going. I'm just going to relax here.~
@8172 = ~[ARAN] Well, are you goin' to join me, or just be on th' look out?~
@8173 = ~[PC] (Strip down to your underthings and carefully wade out into the water.)~
@8174 = ~[PC] You go ahead and swim. I will just keep watch.~
@8175 = ~[ARAN] Now, wait a blighted second, here. You wouldn't be so mean as to make me come out an' get 'em, would you?~
@8176 = ~[PC] (Hide the clothes behind your back, and nod.)~
@8177 = ~[PC] You wouldn't dare. You don't have any clothes on.~
