@8277 = ~[ARAN] (Water streams off of his body as he advances towards you, more and more of his form becoming revealed.)~
@8278 = ~[PC] If you keep that up, you will be showing... too late.~
@8279 = ~[PC] Have a little modesty, and cover up, please.~
@8280 = ~[PC] And here I thought cold water shrunk things.~
@8281 = ~[PC] (Smile at him, lowering your eyelashes... but keep your gaze rested on his form.)~
@8282 = ~[PC] Here. Catch. And meet me back at camp when you have made yourself presentable. (Throw him a towel and walk away.)~
@8283 = ~[ARAN] Well, I'd be bashful, but your eyes seem to enjoy th' show, eh?~
@8284 = ~[PC] What is not to like?~
@8285 = ~[PC] That was rude.~
@8286 = ~[PC] Well, I always thought of painting nudes. Or painting while nude. Or something.~
@8287 = ~[PC] (Smile again, and cover your eyes.)~
@8288 = ~[PC] (Frown at him, looking directly into his face.)~
@8289 = ~[PC] The show seems to be over, at least for now. I am headed back to camp. You should probably head that way yourself.~
@8290 = ~[ARAN] Throw a lad a towel, then, eh?~
@8291 = ~[PC] Here. Catch.~
@8292 = ~[PC] Get your own towel.~
@8293 = ~[PC] One towel. Hmmm. Now, what is that towel worth to you? It is too late to preserve your modesty, if that is what you are worried about.~
@8294 = ~[PC] (Gently cast a towel his way, trying to make sure he can catch it.)~
@8295 = ~[PC] (Throw a towel blindly in his general direction.)~
@8296 = ~[PC] You get your own towel. Just wait until I have headed back to camp, and then you can get out.~
@8297 = ~[ARAN] True enough. Though truth be told, mayhap th' water be less to blame than expectations, eh? I be normal enough.~
@8298 = ~[PC] Things look very... intruiging.~
@8299 = ~[PC] If you are trying to impress me, well, I am not that impressed.~
@8300 = ~[PC] Well, I am not sure what expectations I am supposed to have. Is this a normal subject of conversation for you?~
@8301 = ~[PC] (Blush brightly and look down at your hands.)~
@8302 = ~[PC] (Shake your head in exasperation, frowning at him.)~
