@8308 = ~[PC] (You stand up and brush yourself off, turning your back to him as you walk away.)~
@8309 = ~[ARAN] (From the sounds of things, he makes his way noisily out of the water and picks up his towel.)~
@8310 = ~[PC] I am keeping my eyes averted, but I'd like to be able to see you. Modestly attired, of course. Can I look yet?~
@8311 = ~[PC] Are you trying to get me to picture ~
@8312 = ~[PC] (Blush brightly at the thoughts running through your head.)~
@8313 = ~[PC] (Sniff disdainfully and begin tapping your fingers together impatiently.)~
@8314 = ~[PC] I think I will see you later. I need to get going.~
@8315 = ~[ARAN] Well, one towel brought to shield an' modesty be preserved, an' dryin' off be a right quick accomplishment. I'd have liked to spend a mite bit more time swimmin', but duty calls, eh?~
@8316 = ~[PC] You could take your time drying off, you know. It does some nice things to your muscles.~
@8317 = ~[PC] I am not sure if duty calls or not, but you are taking a rather long time to do something so simple. And don't stare at my backside that way.~
