@10031 = ~[ARAN] Nice tits.~
@10032 = ~[ARAN] That be strange. I feel a right strong compulsion to say what I think, but somethin' tells me that if I do <PLAYER6> will slice my head off. Or you will. Or you both will. I be gettin' a mite bit confused...~
