@12104 = ~[ARAN] Oh, nothin' much. Just th' whole set o' Bhaalspawn tryin' to take power makes me wonder if they have any family feelin's at all. Wholesale slaughter o' innocents seems like it be born o' not havin' a sister around to keep you straight.~
