@12106 = ~[PC] Are you talking about me?~
@12107 = ~[PC] You don't know how much of a curse having a god's blood course through your veins can be. It is a constant struggle, and one mistake can turn every friend you ever had into an enemy. No Bhaalspawn has an easy childhood.~
