@12110 = ~[ARAN] Oh, I think th' amount o' death an' destruction around right now be makin' me a mite nostalgic for happier times. You must be thinkin' somethin' similar, eh?~
@12111 = ~[ARAN] An' why not? Family be family. There be plenty o' reasons to talk about family wi' a boon companion, you know.~
@12112 = ~[ARAN] Now, I said naught o' courtin', at least not you. You an' Elena... there be a right unsound idea. But I were thinkin' more retrospective, I suppose.~
@12113 = ~[ARAN] Aye, my sister she be, an' as far as I can tell I have had naught in th' way o' discussion otherwise. Do you ever listen to me, or do it be more like I talk to the wind an' once in a while you nod so's to humor me?~
