@12116 = ~[PC] I remember Imoen getting into trouble all the time, and somehow dragging me into it. Or was it the other way around? You know, I don't suppose it matters. We were pretty much inseparable.~
@12117 = ~[PC] If by 'family' you mean the man who fostered me and kept me from danger, and the girl who claimed me as her own best friend and sister with no questions asked, yes.~
@12118 = ~[PC] I do have some happy memories of that time. Imoen was a terror, and teased me mercilessly. But she had a big heart, and always tried to help me, too.~
