@12122 = ~[PC] I remember Imoen torturing me and teasing me, bothering me, and generally taking up the attention that was rightfully mine.~
@12123 = ~[PC] If by 'family' you mean the man who fostered me and kept me from my true heritage, and the girl who weighed me down all the time, no.~
@12124 = ~[PC] I do have some happy memories of that time. Imoen was particularly easy to bend to my will. I once had her brainwashed into curtsying every time she began speaking. It was fun.~
@12125 = ~[ARAN] Now that be one hells o' a memory. Sounds like a low self image combined wi' some sort o' feelin's o' entitlement. Feel persecuted much?~
@12126 = ~[PC] Why, yes, actually. Sometimes when you feel like most of existence is out to get you, they actually are.~
@12127 = ~[PC] Did you say something? Because I think you were saying something like "I wish that <CHARNAME> would seal my mouth with tar and use me as an archery target".~
@12128 = ~[PC] Words of deep analysis and introspection from the great Sage of the Dungheap. Has this entire adventure not taught you the strength of my power, and the number of beings interested in possessing it?~
