@12132 = ~[ARAN] Why, you do be right fascinatin'. But family be a powerful thing, an' I was just wonderin', is all...~
@12133 = ~[ARAN] No, no... Look, this be all messed up. I started wi' a thought about how things were wi' my sister Elena in Waterdeep, an' headed off on some memories.~
@12134 = ~[ARAN] I just worry about th' little things, is all. Like whether th' spells she works be safe. Or th' lads she meets, that they be nothin' like me at all, wi' any luck. You had Imoen targeted, an' taken. My worries seem right trivial by comparison, but they be there none th' less.~
