@12142 = ~[ARAN] I just don't rightly know how you dealt wi' th' feelin's about that Irenicus bastard takin' that sister o' yours. It be one thing to have things pushed on you, but on family, that be a heavy burden to carry. Hells, I am jumpy about Elena bein' alone in Waterdeep, an' you had a bit more than that at stake, eh?~
