@12296 = ~[PC] It pains me to say it, but your magic is a necessary part of my party. Come on, and don't dawdle.~
@12297 = ~[PC] Stop pickpocketing me, and you can come along.~
@12298 = ~[PC] I need your lore and inspiring oratory, Aran. Just please stop the whole 'try to teach yourself a stringed instrument" thing. It sounds like cats being thrown in a shower.~
