@12474 = ~[ARAN] I'm not so sure, though. I did some readin' up on Deneir, an' it seems like there's a fair bit o' forward behavior involved. Somethin' about big families, an' practicin' to make 'em. I suspect I shouldn't get that forward wi' you, though.~
